des:
Are you a huge Pittsburgh Pirates fan? Then you need the Rum Bunter Flash Briefing Skill by FanSided to get the latest news, opinions and rumors on the Pittsburgh Pirates. 

The Rum Bunter is a news and opinion site for fans of the Pittsburgh Pirates brought to you by the FanSided Network dedicated to providing top-notch news, views and original content. This site also serves as a community for like-minded fans to come together to catch up on the latest news and to discuss their passion.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
